-- Arnoldo Mondadori Plans to Reorganize Into Three Divisions, Il Sole Says
-- B y   D a n   L i e f g r e e n   a n d   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 2010-10-13T07:21:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/mondadori-ceo-costa-plans-to-revamp-business-in-three-units-sole-reports.html
Publisher Arnoldo Mondadori Editore
SpA Chief Executive Officer Maurizio Costa plans to start a
reorganziation of the company into three divisions by the end of
the year, daily Il Sole 24 Ore reported, citing a letter to
employees. The three units will be publishing, digital and
operations, the newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Liefgreen at 
 dliefgreen@bloomberg.net  